Who took home an Oscar?
USA TODAY movie critic Brian Truitt correctly predicted four out of six key categories.
Who was honored at Hollywood's biggest night, the 88th Academy Awards? Here's a full list of winners and nominees from Sunday's show, hosted by Chris Rock.
When Marnie Was There
Til It Happens to You, from The Hunting Ground
The 100-Year-Old Man Who Climbed out the Window and Disappeared
The Look of Silence
Winner: The Girl on the River: The Price of Forgiveness
We Can't Live Without Cosmos
Everything Will Be Okay